    <div class="acknowledgements-intro">
      <p>Arc^ exists because others paved the way. <strong>Open science movements, community-led research initiatives, and hardware hackers</strong> showed us what's possible.</p>
      <p><strong>We draw inspiration and learn from:</strong></p>
    </div>

